net.proteusframework.ui.management

Annotation Type ApplicationFunction


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Documented
 @Component
 @Scope(value="prototype")
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Qualifier(value="ApplicationFunction")
 @Lazy
public @interface ApplicationFunction
    Defines an application function.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@proteus.co)

        Configuration method. Defaults to "configure".
